data.title: Saint George Church, Old Cairo
data.meta_description: Saint George Church, was built by Athanasius during the reign of Ibn Marwan, Governor of Egypt, and was mentioned in the History of the Patriarchs of the Coptic Church and by Al-Maqrizi. know More .!
